<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<definitions xmlns="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/wsdl/" name="DomainService" targetNamespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" xmlns:tns="http://www.transip.nl/soap" xmlns:impl="http://www.transip.nl/soap" xmlns:xsd1="http://www.transip.nl/soap" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:wsdl="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/wsdl/" xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/wsdl/soap/" xmlns:soapenc="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/">
  <types>
    <schema xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" targetNamespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap">
      <complexType name="ArrayOfstring">
        <complexContent>
          <restriction base="soapenc:Array">
            <attribute ref="soapenc:arrayType" wsdl:arrayType="xsd:string[]"/>
          </restriction>
        </complexContent>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="ArrayOfDomainCheckResult">
        <complexContent>
          <restriction base="soapenc:Array">
            <attribute ref="soapenc:arrayType" wsdl:arrayType="tns:DomainCheckResult[]"/>
          </restriction>
        </complexContent>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="DomainCheckResult">
        <sequence>
          <element name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="status" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="actions" type="tns:ArrayOfstring"/>
        </sequence>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="Domain">
        <sequence>
          <element name="name" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="nameservers" type="tns:ArrayOfNameserver"/>
          <element name="contacts" type="tns:ArrayOfWhoisContact"/>
          <element name="dnsEntries" type="tns:ArrayOfDnsEntry"/>
          <element name="branding" type="tns:DomainBranding"/>
          <element name="authCode" type="xsd:string" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1"/>
          <element name="isLocked" type="xsd:boolean" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1"/>
          <element name="registrationDate" type="xsd:string" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1"/>
          <element name="renewalDate" type="xsd:string" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1"/>
        </sequence>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="ArrayOfNameserver">
        <complexContent>
          <restriction base="soapenc:Array">
            <attribute ref="soapenc:arrayType" wsdl:arrayType="tns:Nameserver[]"/>
          </restriction>
        </complexContent>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="Nameserver">
        <sequence>
          <element name="hostname" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="ipv4" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="ipv6" type="xsd:string"/>
        </sequence>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="ArrayOfWhoisContact">
        <complexContent>
          <restriction base="soapenc:Array">
            <attribute ref="soapenc:arrayType" wsdl:arrayType="tns:WhoisContact[]"/>
          </restriction>
        </complexContent>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="WhoisContact">
        <sequence>
          <element name="type" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="firstName" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="middleName" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="lastName" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="companyName" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="companyKvk" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="companyType" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="street" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="number" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="postalCode" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="city" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="phoneNumber" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="faxNumber" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="email" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="country" type="xsd:string"/>
        </sequence>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="ArrayOfDnsEntry">
        <complexContent>
          <restriction base="soapenc:Array">
            <attribute ref="soapenc:arrayType" wsdl:arrayType="tns:DnsEntry[]"/>
          </restriction>
        </complexContent>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="DnsEntry">
        <sequence>
          <element name="name" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="expire" type="xsd:int"/>
          <element name="type" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="content" type="xsd:string"/>
        </sequence>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="DomainBranding">
        <sequence>
          <element name="companyName" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="supportEmail" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="companyUrl" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="termsOfUsageUrl" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="bannerLine1" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="bannerLine2" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="bannerLine3" type="xsd:string"/>
        </sequence>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="ArrayOfDomain">
        <complexContent>
          <restriction base="soapenc:Array">
            <attribute ref="soapenc:arrayType" wsdl:arrayType="tns:Domain[]"/>
          </restriction>
        </complexContent>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="ArrayOfTld">
        <complexContent>
          <restriction base="soapenc:Array">
            <attribute ref="soapenc:arrayType" wsdl:arrayType="tns:Tld[]"/>
          </restriction>
        </complexContent>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="Tld">
        <sequence>
          <element name="name" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="price" type="xsd:float"/>
          <element name="renewalPrice" type="xsd:float"/>
          <element name="capabilities" type="tns:ArrayOfstring"/>
          <element name="registrationPeriodLength" type="xsd:int"/>
          <element name="cancelTimeFrame" type="xsd:int"/>
        </sequence>
      </complexType>
      <complexType name="DomainAction">
        <sequence>
          <element name="name" type="xsd:string"/>
          <element name="hasFailed" type="xsd:boolean"/>
          <element name="message" type="xsd:string"/>
        </sequence>
      </complexType>
    </schema>
  </types>
  <portType name="DomainServicePortType">
    <operation name="batchCheckAvailability" parameterOrder="domainNames">
      <input message="tns:BatchCheckAvailabilityRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:BatchCheckAvailabilityResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="checkAvailability" parameterOrder="domainName">
      <input message="tns:CheckAvailabilityRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:CheckAvailabilityResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getWhois" parameterOrder="domainName">
      <input message="tns:GetWhoisRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:GetWhoisResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getDomainNames">
      <input message="tns:GetDomainNamesRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:GetDomainNamesResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getInfo" parameterOrder="domainName">
      <input message="tns:GetInfoRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:GetInfoResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="batchGetInfo" parameterOrder="domainNames">
      <input message="tns:BatchGetInfoRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:BatchGetInfoResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getAuthCode" parameterOrder="domainName">
      <input message="tns:GetAuthCodeRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:GetAuthCodeResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getIsLocked" parameterOrder="domainName">
      <input message="tns:GetIsLockedRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:GetIsLockedResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="register" parameterOrder="domain">
      <input message="tns:RegisterRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:RegisterResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="cancel" parameterOrder="domainName endTime">
      <input message="tns:CancelRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:CancelResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="transferWithOwnerChange" parameterOrder="domain authCode">
      <input message="tns:TransferWithOwnerChangeRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:TransferWithOwnerChangeResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="transferWithoutOwnerChange" parameterOrder="domain authCode">
      <input message="tns:TransferWithoutOwnerChangeRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:TransferWithoutOwnerChangeResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setNameservers" parameterOrder="domainName nameservers">
      <input message="tns:SetNameserversRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:SetNameserversResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setLock" parameterOrder="domainName">
      <input message="tns:SetLockRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:SetLockResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="unsetLock" parameterOrder="domainName">
      <input message="tns:UnsetLockRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:UnsetLockResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setDnsEntries" parameterOrder="domainName dnsEntries">
      <input message="tns:SetDnsEntriesRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:SetDnsEntriesResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setOwner" parameterOrder="domainName registrantWhoisContact">
      <input message="tns:SetOwnerRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:SetOwnerResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setContacts" parameterOrder="domainName contacts">
      <input message="tns:SetContactsRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:SetContactsResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getAllTldInfos">
      <input message="tns:GetAllTldInfosRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:GetAllTldInfosResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getTldInfo" parameterOrder="tldName">
      <input message="tns:GetTldInfoRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:GetTldInfoResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getCurrentDomainAction" parameterOrder="domainName">
      <input message="tns:GetCurrentDomainActionRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:GetCurrentDomainActionResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="retryCurrentDomainActionWithNewData" parameterOrder="domain">
      <input message="tns:RetryCurrentDomainActionWithNewDataRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:RetryCurrentDomainActionWithNewDataResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="retryTransferWithDifferentAuthCode" parameterOrder="domain newAuthCode">
      <input message="tns:RetryTransferWithDifferentAuthCodeRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:RetryTransferWithDifferentAuthCodeResponse"/>
    </operation>
    <operation name="cancelDomainAction" parameterOrder="domain">
      <input message="tns:CancelDomainActionRequest"/>
      <output message="tns:CancelDomainActionResponse"/>
    </operation>
  </portType>
  <binding name="DomainServiceBinding" type="tns:DomainServicePortType">
    <soap:binding style="rpc" transport="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/http"/>
    <operation name="batchCheckAvailability">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#batchCheckAvailability"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainNames" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="checkAvailability">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#checkAvailability"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getWhois">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#getWhois"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getDomainNames">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#getDomainNames"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getInfo">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#getInfo"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="batchGetInfo">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#batchGetInfo"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainNames" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getAuthCode">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#getAuthCode"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getIsLocked">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#getIsLocked"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="register">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#register"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domain" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="cancel">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#cancel"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName endTime" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="transferWithOwnerChange">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#transferWithOwnerChange"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domain authCode" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="transferWithoutOwnerChange">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#transferWithoutOwnerChange"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domain authCode" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setNameservers">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#setNameservers"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName nameservers" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setLock">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#setLock"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="unsetLock">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#unsetLock"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setDnsEntries">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#setDnsEntries"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName dnsEntries" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setOwner">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#setOwner"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName registrantWhoisContact" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="setContacts">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#setContacts"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName contacts" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getAllTldInfos">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#getAllTldInfos"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getTldInfo">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#getTldInfo"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="tldName" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="getCurrentDomainAction">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#getCurrentDomainAction"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domainName" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body parts="return" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="retryCurrentDomainActionWithNewData">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#retryCurrentDomainActionWithNewData"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domain" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="retryTransferWithDifferentAuthCode">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#retryTransferWithDifferentAuthCode"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domain newAuthCode" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>
    </operation>
    <operation name="cancelDomainAction">
      <soap:operation soapAction="urn:DomainService#DomainServiceServer#cancelDomainAction"/>
      <input>
        <soap:body parts="domain" use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </input>
      <output>
        <soap:body use="encoded" namespace="http://www.transip.nl/soap" encodingStyle="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/encoding/"/>
      </output>

  <message name="BatchCheckAvailabilityRequest">
    <part name="domainNames" type="tns:ArrayOfstring"/>
  </message>
  <message name="BatchCheckAvailabilityResponse">
    <part name="return" type="tns:ArrayOfDomainCheckResult"/>
  </message>
  <message name="CheckAvailabilityRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="CheckAvailabilityResponse">
    <part name="return" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="GetWhoisRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="GetWhoisResponse">
    <part name="return" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="GetDomainNamesRequest"/>
  <message name="GetDomainNamesResponse">
    <part name="return" type="tns:ArrayOfstring"/>
  </message>
  <message name="GetInfoRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="GetInfoResponse">
    <part name="return" type="tns:Domain"/>
  </message>
  <message name="BatchGetInfoRequest">
    <part name="domainNames" type="tns:ArrayOfstring"/>
  </message>
  <message name="BatchGetInfoResponse">
    <part name="return" type="tns:ArrayOfDomain"/>
  </message>
  <message name="GetAuthCodeRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="GetAuthCodeResponse">
    <part name="return" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="GetIsLockedRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="GetIsLockedResponse">
    <part name="return" type="xsd:boolean"/>
  </message>
  <message name="RegisterRequest">
    <part name="domain" type="tns:Domain"/>
  </message>
  <message name="RegisterResponse"/>
  <message name="CancelRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
    <part name="endTime" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="CancelResponse"/>
  <message name="TransferWithOwnerChangeRequest">
    <part name="domain" type="tns:Domain"/>
    <part name="authCode" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="TransferWithOwnerChangeResponse"/>
  <message name="TransferWithoutOwnerChangeRequest">
    <part name="domain" type="tns:Domain"/>
    <part name="authCode" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="TransferWithoutOwnerChangeResponse"/>
  <message name="SetNameserversRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
    <part name="nameservers" type="tns:ArrayOfNameserver"/>
  </message>
  <message name="SetNameserversResponse"/>
  <message name="SetLockRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="SetLockResponse"/>
  <message name="UnsetLockRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
  </message>
  <message name="UnsetLockResponse"/>
  <message name="SetDnsEntriesRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
    <part name="dnsEntries" type="tns:ArrayOfDnsEntry"/>
  </message>
  <message name="SetDnsEntriesResponse"/>
  <message name="SetOwnerRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
    <part name="registrantWhoisContact" type="tns:WhoisContact"/>
  </message>
  <message name="SetOwnerResponse"/>
  <message name="SetContactsRequest">
    <part name="domainName" type="xsd:string"/>
    <part name="contacts" type="tns:ArrayOfWhoisContact"/>
  </message>
  <message name="SetContactsResponse"/>
  <message name="GetAllTldInfosRequest"/>
  <message name="GetAllTldInfosResponse">
    <part name="return" type="tns:ArrayOfTld"/>
